<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>We miss you!</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { background:#f0f4f8; font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color:#333; padding: 20px 0; }
    .container { max-width:560px; margin:0 auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 6px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.09); }
    .header { background:linear-gradient(140deg, #0f2d5e 0%, #1a56db 100%); padding:44px 40px 36px; text-align:center; }
    .header .wave { font-size:52px; display:block; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .header h1 { color:#ffffff; font-size:24px; font-weight:800; margin:0; letter-spacing:-0.3px; }
    .header p  { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size:14px; margin-top:6px; }
    .body { padding:40px; }
    .intro { font-size:16px; color:#374151; line-height:1.65; margin-bottom:24px; }
    .intro strong { color:#0f2d5e; }
    .stats-row { display:flex; gap:16px; margin-bottom:28px; }
    .stat-card { flex:1; background:#f8faff; border:1px solid #dbe4ff; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; text-align:center; }
    .stat-card .number { font-size:26px; font-weight:800; color:#1a56db; }
    .stat-card .label  { font-size:11px; color:#6b7280; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.8px; margin-top:4px; }
    .highlight { background:#fefce8; border:1px solid #fef08a; border-radius:10px; padding:18px 20px; margin-bottom:28px; font-size:14px; color:#713f12; line-height:1.6; }
    .highlight strong { color:#92400e; }
    .cta { text-align:center; margin:28px 0 8px; }
    .cta a { display:inline-block; background:#1a56db; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; padding:16px 44px; border-radius:10px; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.3px; }
    .cta a:hover { background:#1447c0; }
    .sub-cta { text-align:center; font-size:13px; color:#9ca3af; margin-top:12px; }
    .divider { border:none; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; margin:28px 0; }
    .features { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; margin-bottom:24px; }
    .feature { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; }
    .feature .icon { font-size:22px; flex-shrink:0; }
    .feature .text { font-size:14px; color:#4b5563; line-height:1.5; }
    .feature .text strong { color:#1f2937; display:block; margin-bottom:2px; }
    .footer { background:#f8f9fb; padding:20px 40px; text-align:center; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer p { font-size:12px; color:#9ca3af; line-height:1.8; }
    .footer a { color:#6b7280; text-decoration:none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="wave">👋</span>
      <h1>We miss you, {{user_name}}!</h1>
      <p>Your academic journey is waiting for you</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p class="intro">
        It's been a while since we've seen you on <strong>FuhsoX</strong>. Your classmates are still practising,
        streaks are being built, and exam season doesn't wait for anyone.
      </p>

      {{#if trending_topic}}
      <div class="highlight">
        🔥 <strong>Trending right now:</strong> Students in your faculty are actively practising
        <strong>{{trending_topic}}</strong> — don't get left behind.
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon">📚</div>
          <div class="text">
            <strong>Past Questions Ready</strong>
            Thousands of exam questions organised by course, year and difficulty — pick up right where you left off.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon">🤖</div>
          <div class="text">
            <strong>AI-Powered Feedback</strong>
            Get instant, personalised explanations every time you answer a question wrong.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="icon">🏆</div>
          <div class="text">
            <strong>Compete with Peers</strong>
            See where you stand on the leaderboard — your ranking is waiting to be reclaimed.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="{{cta_link}}">Resume Your Preparation →</a>
      </div>
      <p class="sub-cta">Takes less than 30 seconds to get back on track.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        &copy; {{year}} {{institution_name}} &middot; Powered by FuhsoX<br/>
        You received this because you have an account with FuhsoX.<br/>
        <a href="#">Unsubscribe from re-engagement emails</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
